???  remember no matter what they tell you the Manual and auto tranny
axles are DIFFERENT lengths..and are NOT interchangable.

half shaft length

manual      476mm  (18 3/4in)
auto left   457mm  (18 in)
auto right  505mm  (19 7/8 in)

